{"TopicId":141498,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Keeping borderless windows open","CreatedByName":"XrayLima","CreatedById":88466,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-09T11:11:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"XrayLima","CreatedById":88466,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-09T11:11:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.3999996185303px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;float:none;background-color:rgb(251,251,251);\u0022\u003EIs there a way of keeping the borderless window (created with the\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.3999996185303px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;float:none;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E-popupwindow\u003C/span\u003E command line arguement)\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.3999996185303px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;float:none;background-color:rgb(251,251,251);\u0022\u003E\u00A0open if I select another program (in my case on a second monitor?). \u00A0I\u0027d like to keep KSP visable, but browse the web whilst I wait for transfer windows etc, but at the moment it minimises the KSP window whenever it isn\u0027t the actively selected program.\u00A0 I\u0027m guessing this will be a Windows setting (10 in my case) so not a Squad issue per se, but if you know where the setting is hiding?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.3999996185303px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;float:none;background-color:rgb(251,251,251);\u0022\u003EAny Ideas?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTa in advance!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nXL\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ibanix","CreatedById":147140,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-09T19:50:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUse -popupwindow with game setting of fullscreen = false. This works for me (Windows 10).\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Val","CreatedById":126227,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-10T09:34:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222623627\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022141498\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221465470688\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002288466\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022XrayLima\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 hours ago, XrayLima said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nat the moment it minimises the KSP window whenever it isn\u0027t the actively selected program\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis happens because KSP is set to Fullscreen in the Graphics settings. Change it to Windowed and it\u0027ll stop minimizing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"XrayLima","CreatedById":88466,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-11T16:55:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/126227-val/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022126227\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/126227-val/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Val\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0You are a steely eyed missile sentient being!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}